					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In that case:<br /><br /><img src="http://www.circuitstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/2-Input-Diode-AND-Gate.jpg" alt="Image" /><br />(just a schematic illustrating what was just described)<br /><br /><br />Note that you can add any amount of inputs (with a diode each)to be AND/OR:ed in these blocks, not just only the two illustrated.. even if that's what we want here.</div>

					
